# CustomerVoice Public Portal — Comprehensive Enhancement Plan

## Executive Summary

This plan transforms the CustomerVoice public portal from a basic read-and-vote interface into a **world-class, multi-use-case feedback platform** rivaling Microsoft Feedback Portal, UserVoice, ProductBoard, and Canny. The plan is organized in **3 phases**, each independently deployable, covering 7 distinct use case archetypes.

---

## Use Case Archetypes

Before listing gaps, we define the diverse personas and contexts this portal must serve:

| # | Use Case | Example | Key Requirements |
|---|----------|---------|------------------|
| 1 | **B2B SaaS Feedback** | Atlassian feature requests | Signed-in users, filtered by product/platform, categories, follow/subscribe, official responses |
| 2 | **Enterprise Employee Feedback** | Internal HR suggestion box | Private portal (domain-restricted), anonymous option, manager-only categories |
| 3 | **Political/Government** | GOV.uk public consultations | Fully public, no sign-in needed to view, anonymous voting, share buttons for social amplification |
| 4 | **B2C Consumer Tech** | Apple/Google feature requests | Massive scale, platform filters (iOS/Android/Web), star/favorite, sign-in via social OAuth |
| 5 | **Open Source Community** | VS Code feature requests | Public, GitHub-like, community-driven, rich commenting threads |
| 6 | **Internal Product Team** | PM prioritization board | Private, RICE scoring visible, admin controls, roadmap view |
| 7 | **Customer Advisory Board** | Invite-only enterprise panel | Access-by-link + email whitelist, NDA-protected ideas, restricted commenting |

---

## Gap Analysis: Current Portal vs Competitors

### Current CustomerVoice Portal Capabilities
- ✅ View ideas list with vote counts
- ✅ Search ideas by keyword
- ✅ Filter by pre-defined status tabs (All, New, Planned, In Progress, Completed)
- ✅ Filter by categories (sidebar)
- ✅ Sort by Top Voted / Most Discussed / Newest
- ✅ Anonymous voting (visitor-id based)
- ✅ Read-only detail slide-over with comments
- ✅ Board description banner

### Missing Features (Gap Analysis)

| # | Feature | Microsoft | UserVoice | Canny | Current | Gap |
|---|---------|-----------|-----------|-------|---------|-----|
| 1 | **Submit new idea** from portal | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | **Critical** |
| 2 | **Post comments** from portal | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | **Critical** |
| 3 | **Share button** (copy link, social) | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | **High** |
| 4 | **Follow/Subscribe** to an idea | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | **High** |
| 5 | **Star/Favorite** ideas | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | **High** |
| 6 | **User authentication** (sign-in/sign-up) | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | **Critical** |
| 7 | **Anonymous vs authenticated** (admin toggle) | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | **Critical** |
| 8 | **Dynamic filters** based on fields | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ (hardcoded) | **High** |
| 9 | **Platform/tag filter** | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | **Medium** |
| 10 | **Official response** badge | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | **Medium** |
| 11 | **Portal access modes** (public/link/private/domain) | Partial | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ (public only) | **Critical** |
| 12 | **Pagination / infinite scroll** | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | **Medium** |
| 13 | **Idea detail full page** (not just slide-over) | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | **Medium** |
| 14 | **Status change notifications** to followers | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | **Medium** |
| 15 | **Duplicate detection** on submit | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | **Low** |
| 16 | **Rich text / markdown** in descriptions | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | **Low** |
| 17 | **Custom branding** (logo, colors) | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | **Medium** |
| 18 | **Changelog / "What's New"** section | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | **Low** |
| 19 | **Mobile responsive** design | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | Partial | **Medium** |
| 20 | **Voter identity display** (avatar, name) | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | **Medium** |

