│  [Dark mode for the dashboard               ]  │
│                                                 │
│  Description:                                   │
│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐│
│  │ I would love to have a dark mode option    ││
│  │ for the dashboard to reduce eye strain     ││
│  │ during late-night work sessions.           ││
│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────┘│
