**Duplicate Detection**: As user types the title, search existing ideas and show matches (client-side debounced search using existing `/ideas?search=` endpoint).

### 1.4 Public Commenting

#### Backend Changes

**New API route in [public.ts](file:///Users/ashishnigam/Startups/CustomerVoice/apps/api/src/routes/public.ts):**

```
POST /public/boards/:boardSlug/ideas/:ideaId/comments
Body: { body, authorEmail?, authorName? }
```

- Checks `board_settings.enable_commenting` and auth requirements
- Respects `idea.comments_locked` flag
- Returns created comment

