### 1.5 Share Functionality

#### UI: Share Button on Each Idea Card + Detail Panel

```
[Share ↗]  →  Dropdown:
┌──────────────────────────┐
│  📋 Copy link            │
│  🐦 Share on Twitter/X   │
│  💼 Share on LinkedIn    │
│  📧 Share via Email      │
└──────────────────────────┘
```

- Copy link generates `{origin}/portal/boards/{slug}/ideas/{ideaId}`
- Social share opens pre-filled share URLs
- Email share opens `mailto:` with subject and link
- No backend changes needed (pure frontend)

#### Backend Change for Deep Links:
```
GET /public/boards/:boardSlug/ideas/:ideaId  (already exists)
```
The portal needs to handle URL routing: `/portal/boards/:slug/ideas/:ideaId` should auto-open the detail panel for that idea.

### 1.6 Dynamic Filters

Replace hardcoded status tabs with dynamic filter bar driven by board settings and available data.

#### UI: Filter Bar

```
┌─ Filters ──────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Status: [All ▼]  Category: [All ▼]  Platform: [All ▼]  │
│ Tags: [Any ▼]    Date: [Any time ▼]                     │
│                                                         │
│ Active filters: [Status: Planned ✕] [Category: UX ✕]   │
│                 [Clear all filters]                      │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

- Filters are generated from the actual data (API returns available statuses, categories, tags)
- Admin controls which filters are visible via `board_settings`
- Tag/Platform requires new `idea_tags` table (see below)

**New table:**
```sql
CREATE TABLE idea_tags (
  id              TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
  workspace_id    TEXT NOT NULL REFERENCES workspaces(id),
  name            TEXT NOT NULL,
  tag_type        TEXT DEFAULT 'general',  -- 'platform', 'priority', 'custom'
  color_hex       TEXT,
  created_at      TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW(),
  UNIQUE(workspace_id, name)
);

CREATE TABLE idea_tag_links (
  idea_id    TEXT NOT NULL REFERENCES ideas(id),
  tag_id     TEXT NOT NULL REFERENCES idea_tags(id),
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW(),
  PRIMARY KEY(idea_id, tag_id)
);
```

### Phase 1 Summary of Changes

#### Database Migrations (new migration `005_portal_access_and_engagement`)
- `board_settings` table
- `portal_users` table
- `portal_sessions` table
- `idea_tags` + `idea_tag_links` tables

#### API Routes (additions to [public.ts](file:///Users/ashishnigam/Startups/CustomerVoice/apps/api/src/routes/public.ts))
- `GET /public/boards/:boardSlug/settings` — returns portal config
- `POST /public/auth/register`
- `POST /public/auth/login`
- `POST /public/auth/magic-link`
- `GET /public/auth/me`
- `POST /public/auth/logout`
- `POST /public/boards/:boardSlug/ideas` — submit new idea
- `POST /public/boards/:boardSlug/ideas/:ideaId/comments` — post comment
- `GET /public/boards/:boardSlug/tags` — list available tags

#### Admin Dashboard Changes ([PortalApp.tsx](file:///Users/ashishnigam/Startups/CustomerVoice/apps/web/src/PortalApp.tsx))
- New "Portal Settings" tab for each board
- Board settings form with access mode, auth toggles, branding

#### Public Portal Changes ([CustomerPortal.tsx](file:///Users/ashishnigam/Startups/CustomerVoice/apps/web/src/CustomerPortal.tsx))
- Auth modal (sign-in/sign-up)
- Submit idea button + modal with duplicate detection
- Comment posting in detail panel
- Share dropdown on idea cards and detail panel
- Dynamic filter bar replacing hardcoded status tabs
- Deep link support for `/portal/boards/:slug/ideas/:ideaId`
- Auth-gated actions (vote/comment/submit based on board settings)
- Session persistence in localStorage

