## Phase 2: Engagement & Personalization — Follow, Favorite, Notifications, Full Detail Page

**Timeline:** Sprint 4-6 | **Priority:** High | **Goal:** Keep users engaged and coming back

### 2.1 Follow/Subscribe to Ideas

#### Backend Changes

**New table:**
```sql
CREATE TABLE idea_subscriptions (
  idea_id         TEXT NOT NULL REFERENCES ideas(id),
  user_id         TEXT NOT NULL REFERENCES portal_users(id),
  notify_on       TEXT[] DEFAULT ARRAY['status_change', 'official_response', 'new_comment'],
  created_at      TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW(),
  PRIMARY KEY(idea_id, user_id)
);
```

**New API routes:**
```
POST   /public/boards/:boardSlug/ideas/:ideaId/subscribe
DELETE /public/boards/:boardSlug/ideas/:ideaId/subscribe
GET    /public/me/subscriptions  — list all followed ideas
```

#### UI: Follow Button

On each idea card and in the detail panel:
```
[🔔 Follow]  →  toggles to  [🔔 Following ✓]
```

When clicked while not following:
```
┌───────────────────────────────────┐
│  🔔 Follow this idea             │
│                                   │
│  Notify me when:                  │
│  ☑ Status changes                 │
│  ☑ Official response posted       │
│  ☑ New comments added             │
│                                   │
│  [Follow]                         │
└───────────────────────────────────┘
```

### 2.2 Star/Favorite Ideas

#### Backend Changes

**New table:**
```sql
CREATE TABLE idea_favorites (
  idea_id    TEXT NOT NULL REFERENCES ideas(id),
  user_id    TEXT NOT NULL REFERENCES portal_users(id),
  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW(),
  PRIMARY KEY(idea_id, user_id)
);
```

**New API routes:**
```
POST   /public/boards/:boardSlug/ideas/:ideaId/favorite
DELETE /public/boards/:boardSlug/ideas/:ideaId/favorite
GET    /public/me/favorites  — list user's favorited ideas
```

#### UI: Star Icon

```
Each idea card:  ☆ (empty) → ★ (filled, golden)
```

A new sidebar tab: **"My Favorites"** that shows only favorited ideas.

### 2.3 Full Idea Detail Page

Instead of only a slide-over panel, support a full-page detail view at `/portal/boards/:slug/ideas/:ideaId`.

